right|thumb|cover page of first edition ( 1853)thumb|1921 edition illustrated by virginia frances sterrett tanglewood tales for boys and girls ( 1853 ) is a book by american author nathaniel hawthorne , a sequel to a wonder - book for girls and boys .

authors & their works : " the pygmies " & " the pomegranate seeds " are 2 of his " tanglewood tales "

